caddy安装 Debian、Ubuntu、Raspbian 
sudo apt install -y debian-keyring debian-archive-keyring apt-transport-https
curl -1sLf 'https://dl.cloudsmith.io/public/caddy/stable/gpg.key' | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/caddy-stable-archive-keyring.gpg
curl -1sLf 'https://dl.cloudsmith.io/public/caddy/stable/debian.deb.txt' | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/caddy-stable.list
sudo apt update
sudo apt install caddy

启动服务
systemctl start caddy
systemctl stop caddy
配置重载
systemctl reload caddy
服务状态
systemctl status caddy
格式CADDY
caddy fmt /etc/caddy/Caddyfile --overwrite

证书路径
/var/lib/caddy/.local/share/caddy/certificates/acme-v02.api.letsencrypt.org-directory目录下

https://github.com/lxhao61/integrated-examples/releases/download/20231012/caddy-linux-amd64.tar.gz
$ chmod +x caddy
$ mv caddy /usr/bin/
